vgy - Video Get Youtube Channel

USAGE:
    vgy

DESCRIPTION:
    Fetch videos from configured YouTube channels, apply filters,
    and queue matching videos for download. Processes all configured
    channels according to their specific filtering rules.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-videos-youtube-channels CHANNELS
        Space-separated list of YouTube channel IDs

    -conf-videos-yt-days-back DAYS
        How many days back to fetch (default: 7)

    -conf-videos-yt-max-results NUM
        Maximum results per page (default: 50)

    -conf-videos-yt-max-pages NUM
        Maximum pages to fetch (default: 5)

    -conf-videos-yt-order ORDER
        Order of results (default: date)

    -conf-videos-yt-type TYPE
        Type of results (default: video)

    -conf-yt-api-key KEY
        YouTube API key (required)

EXAMPLES:
    vgy

    _youtube_channel_filter must be defined in your ~/.config/walterjwhite/shell/videos configuration which determines what files should be downloaded and what format
    